<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-7883] XSD decoding bad guess in Validator</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-7883</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Validator component does not take imported XSD encoding into account when validating XML. That may lead to validation errors if an imported XSD is ISO-8859-1 encoded and containing non ASCII caracters, even though that XSD declares its encoding correctly in its XML prolog.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12745099">CAMEL-7883</key>
